name: Banned In China 1.01
description: Series of 100 works I am making that will be virtual flags that can be used in various Ethereum and other blockchain virtual worlds. Make a virtual statement and be proud of being banned in China, it's how freedom rings. I also developed with inspiration from the 90s 'Parental Advisory' sticker so feel free to stick it on your meta-building and be proud of resisting oppression, wherever it may come from.
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. SuperRare's smart contract platform allows artists to release limited-edition digital artwork tracked on the blockchain, making the pieces rare, verified, and collectible. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
